tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE medication_orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    prescriber_id INT,
    medication_name TEXT,
    dosage FLOAT,
    order_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE MedicationOrders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    medication_name VARCHAR(50),
    dosage FLOAT,
    date_ordered DATE
);

CREATE TABLE DrugInteractions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    medication1 VARCHAR(50),
    medication2 VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Medications (
    medication_id UUID NOT NULL,
    medication_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    dosage FLOAT NOT NULL,
    prescribing_physician_id UUID NOT NULL,
    prescription_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (medication_id)
);

CREATE TABLE DrugInteractions (
    interaction_id UUID NOT NULL,
    medication1_id UUID NOT NULL,
    medication2_id UUID NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    interaction_description TEXT NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (interaction_id)
);

    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
